title: [Whistler's Pass, Grassy Field]
description: Incredibly, the fog thickens further down the trail.  Marked by moisture from the fog's passing, a few patches of tall grasses can just barely be seen off the trail, their wet blades sparkling like stars in the darkness.  The grade of the trail levels out more with its descent.
